Title: Network topology and BI visualization: fix node highlighting and selection
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1632140805
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

Nodes are now highlighted again, if the mouse hovers over entries in the
dropdown of search results. Additionally, it is possible to select a node
with a click on an entry in the search results, again.
